', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/87077/', '', 'Rimegepant, Eptinezumab, Ubrogepant, Galcanezumab, Atogepant, Methysergide, Erenumab, Fremanezumab', 'Halothane, Thiopental, Sodium oxybate, Isoflurane, Methohexital, Nitrous oxide, Desflurane, Propofol, Enflurane, Esketamine, Sevoflurane, Etomidate', 1767369485);
